Mpa kugenda Mwami, Nca aho Waciye, Mu nzir-ijana mw’Ijuru;
Nzan-umunezero Mu batitaweho, Wam-Unyuzuz-urukundo.

Chœur :
Wam-Unyuzuz-urukundo Uko ngendana n’inuma Umpe kwama ngenda Ndirimba nezerewe Wam-Unyuzuz-urukundo.

Name ndi kumwe N’Umukiz-Anyobora, Ntundekere mu mwijima;
Ndinda ukuraka, Nezerwe mu mutima, Wam-Unyuzuz-urukundo.

Ngiye guheza vub- Urugendo rwanje, Nziber-iwacu mw’Ijuru;
Ngane ku nkombe Ndirimba nshim-Umwami, Wam-Unyuzuz-urukundo.

Umutima wanj-urera Nk’agashurwe, nk’urubura;
Usa neza nk’umugezi, Uhwahutse nk’inyoni.
