N-isezerano ry’imvur-ihereza;
Rangamiza rab-ingano zeze: Ibitangaza kw’Izina rya Yesu.
Munywe bantu banj-imvur-ihereza.

Ndushaho gukunda Yesu, (x2)
Imisi yose, kugez-Agarutse;
